description.default: SimplePlan is a simple and efficient to-do list software that provides you with a seamless experience of easily managing tasks and plans. From creating tasks in real-time to quickly viewing schedules, everything has become effortless.
description.zh_CN: 快捷计划是一款简单而高效的待办清单软件，为您提供轻松管理任务和计划的无缝体验。从即时创建任务到快速查看日程，一切都变得轻而易举。
